objToCat[source]

objToCat(df)

This function make objective column to categories and replace with int8 code Note: This Function Need import DataFrame with pandas

### Example

>>> dataframe.info()
>>> i Name_Column Len Dtype: object
...
>>> objToCat(dataframe)
>>> dataframe.info()
>>> i Name_Column Len Dtype: int8

Sign: mkarimi21

sampleDF[source]

sampleDF(df, column)

Clean Data and make equal labale for classfication

# Example

>>> list(DataFrame['Column'].value_counts())
>>> [Alpha, Beta, ...]
...
>>> a = sampleDF(DataFrame, 'Column')
>>> list(a.value_counts())
>>> [N, N, N, ...]

Sign: mkarimi21
